Class UserPanel

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class UserPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    UserPanel is a JPanel. It accounts for a user view. It accepts an user id to follow, a tweet, and shows news feed.
